title: That's My Bush DVDrips and Commentaries
description:
i actually bought the dvd set of this just so i could upload it! i ripped all of the episodes and the commentaries from matt and trey and the cast.

by the way, in case you didn't know, this is made by the same people who make south park

this is everything that is on the dvds, and it's smaller than the DVDRs, which is why i did it this way, but if anyone wants the DVDRs, please request them

please be patient, i have a slow connection, and comment and help seed when you're done!
